data.description: This 2019 build by Happe Homes home has so much to offer. With a preferable location tucked back on a quiet street, a vacant lot behind and next to the home, and a great layout! This home has a modern farmhouse feel and all the functionality you need to host your family and friends. All the major necessities are on the main level making this an excellent home for any stage of life. You will immediately feel at home when you walk into the inviting and spacious foyer. That will lead you into an open concept kitchen, dinning room and living room. This gorgeous kitchen has upgraded, chef-like appliances, a spacious island with additional seating, a formal dinning room and a fabulous walk in pantry! You will also love the layout of the spacious primary bedroom and ensuite. There is so much space to enjoy hanging out or entertaining. The covered porch that overlooks a fully fenced in yard, the spacious entertainment room in the basement that also features a fully functioning wet bar! You will also want to check out the attached 3 car garage where you can walk into a well organized mud room and main floor laundry room.
